  - verification
  - knowledge-graph
  - deterministic
  - mcp
abstract: >-
  SIGMA Guard detects structural contradictions in knowledge graphs,
  agent state, and LLM output using cellular sheaf cohomology. It
  identifies global inconsistencies that schema validation and
  constraint engines miss, returning deterministic proof receipts
  with exact contradiction locations and severity rankings. The
  full SIGMA engine achieves 35 microsecond median per-edit latency
  at 5 million vertices with zero drift and zero ML dependency.
